	* XmlValidatingReader.cs: Added deprecation message.

2004-09-14  Atsushi Enomoto  <atsushi@ximian.com>

	* XmlTextWriter.cs : Close() should not Flush() when the output is
	  already closed. bug #65918 is fixed.

