	W3C DOM compliant read-only check support (buggy part in MS.NET).
	* XmlAttribute.cs,
	  XmlCDataSection.cs,
	  XmlCharacterData.cs,
	  XmlDocument.cs,
	  XmlElement.cs,
	  XmlNode.cs,
	  XmlSignificantWhitespace.cs,
	  XmlText.cs
	  : CloneNode() - set read-only when copied node is read-only.
	    Check IsReadOnly on attempt to modify value.
