	* DTDObjectModel.cs, DTDReader.cs, XmlSecureResolver.cs :
	  avoiding obvious exception.
	* DTDReader.cs, XmlTextReader.cs : Some optimization. 
	  Avoided extraneous PeekChar() and reduced name string creation.

