	* XmlAttributeCollection.cs,
	  XmlElement.cs : Fixed bug #51415.
	  When adding attribute to an element using Attributes, it failed.

2003-12-11  Atsushi Enomoto  <ginga@kit.hi-ho.ne.jp>

